keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map k scrollDown
map i scrollUp
map K scrollPageDown
map I scrollPageUp
map - performBackwardsFind
map = performFind
map j goBack
map l goForward
map J previousTab
map L nextTab
map a enterInsertMode
map u restoreTab
map e Vomnibar.activate
map E Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
